name: Runic Screechers of the Depths
description: There are Rootmason carvings all over the heirlooms of the Runic Screechers of the Depths  . Why? How? They're also known to dive deep for treasures and marine resources. Now guiding travelers that attempt to cross the continent in the dead of night, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
